accident during a pro-government demonstration by members of the ruling
Pakistan's People's party who were protesting against the strikes.
The strike was the latest episode in an campaign by Mr Sharif who is
demanding the resignation of Ms Benazir Bhutto, the prime minister, and Mr
Farooq Leghari, the president.
