   MONTREAL
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
Cambior, the Canadian miner, has moved into Argentina by buying 40 per cent
of Pachon Minera, owner of the El Pachon copper property in San Juan
province, writes Robert Gibbens in Montreal.
Minera San Jose, an Argentine company, sold the interest for Dollars 10m.
